        "text_zN6LHh": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We know that running a successful care facility involves balancing high-quality care with efficient operations.\u2028<\/p>\n<p>That’s why we developed <span style=\"color:#350078;font-weight: 500;\">Homecare View<\/span>, an innovative platform that simplifies processes, reduces costs, and provides the control and visibility needed to focus on what matters most, your residents’ well-being.<\/p>",
